00:32:08,650 --> 00:32:11,370
Can I sleep over, please?

512
00:32:11,370 --> 00:32:12,610
Please.

513
00:32:12,610 --> 00:32:14,410
Why don't you ask the others?

514
00:32:14,410 --> 00:32:16,610
Is your house available?

515
00:32:20,270 --> 00:32:22,460
Let's just toast.

516
00:32:23,900 --> 00:32:26,100
Hello, Ai'Nic. What's up?

517
00:32:26,100 --> 00:32:27,480
Where are you right now?

518
00:32:27,480 --> 00:32:29,930
I'm at a bar. I'm taking care of a drunk freshman.

519
00:32:29,930 --> 00:32:32,000
P'No, what time are you coming back?

520
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:34,380
It'll be whatever time it is.

521
00:32:34,380 --> 00:32:37,200
Can you give me a specific time?

522
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:39,810
Hey, you are my little brother. Not my mom.

523
00:32:39,810 --> 00:32:43,120
Oh, come on, P'No. Just tell me, please.

524
00:32:43,120 --> 00:32:45,940
Then I probably won't be back. I have to take care of the drunk freshman.

525
00:32:45,940 --> 00:32:49,170
Tell Mom for me, okay? Later.

526
00:32:51,120 --> 00:32:52,900
What's with him lately?

527
00:32:52,900 --> 00:32:54,900
He's been on me even more than Mom.

528
00:32:54,900 --> 00:32:56,420
Whatever.

529
00:33:00,700 --> 00:33:02,940
So, my big brother isn't coming home.

530
00:33:03,540 --> 00:33:05,730
Yeah, I heard that.

531
00:33:06,850 --> 00:33:10,180
Then you should go home, Ai'Kla.

532
00:33:13,230 --> 00:33:16,220
Who's the underclassman that P'No has to drop off?

533
00:33:16,220 --> 00:33:20,030
Who the hell is he? I'm starting to hate him now.

534
00:33:20,030 --> 00:33:23,820
I see you just hating anyone who gets close to my older brother.

535
00:33:25,670 --> 00:33:30,640
Or should I put him in bed and finish him already?

536
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:31,810
Are you serious?

537
00:33:31,810 --> 00:33:33,070
What?

538
00:33:33,070 --> 00:33:34,870
It's gotten this far, and I'm not going to take it seriously?

539
00:33:34,870 --> 00:33:36,630
And you have to help me, too.

540
00:33:36,630 --> 00:33:39,830
Stop right there. I'd like not to get involved with this.

541
00:33:40,500 --> 00:33:43,030
I have a business proposal for you on this.

542
00:33:43,030 --> 00:33:45,610
Is it going to be a deal or not?

543
00:33:46,470 --> 00:33:48,340
Of course, it's a deal.

544
00:33:49,520 --> 00:33:50,720
You're pretty easy, dude.

545
00:33:50,720 --> 00:33:51,780
Of course, I'm easy.

546
00:33:51,780 --> 00:33:53,680
It's settled.

547
00:34:15,030 --> 00:34:17,410
