551
00:34:24,010 --> 00:34:26,960
Well, my mom is the one who wanted you to come.

552
00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:29,820
But I came here empty-handed. I don't have a single gift at all.

553
00:34:29,820 --> 00:34:34,250
It's all right. Just you coming here is already the best gift.

554
00:34:34,250 --> 00:34:35,980
Hold on.

555
00:34:35,980 --> 00:34:38,620
Is that a gift for you or for your mom?

556
00:34:38,620 --> 00:34:39,920
For Mom, of course.

557
00:34:39,920 --> 00:34:44,730
Well, Mom wanted you to come. If you came, it's only normal for her to be happy.

558
00:34:57,430 --> 00:35:02,980
Actually, I'm the one that wanted you to come.

559
00:35:03,740 --> 00:35:07,360
You're always making yourself to be so cute, Ai'Koon Chai.

560
00:35:07,360 --> 00:35:13,820
