621
00:40:20,270 --> 00:40:22,230
So where is Pete, dear?

622
00:40:25,429 --> 00:40:27,539
The roses, huh?

623
00:40:29,274 --> 00:40:32,376
Ai'Pete does this every year?

624
00:40:32,376 --> 00:40:34,155
Yes.

625
00:40:34,155 --> 00:40:36,645
The first year I saw it,

626
00:40:36,670 --> 00:40:38,160
my heart was going to stop.

627
00:40:38,160 --> 00:40:40,830
His hands were covered with blood and wounds all over.

628
00:40:40,830 --> 00:40:43,780
I should've hit him until it left marks on his butt.

629
00:40:47,100 --> 00:40:50,300
Ai'Pete is really happy to be able to do it for you, Auntie, really.

630
00:40:56,830 --> 00:40:58,760
Yes.

631
00:40:58,760 --> 00:41:03,480
I know that... Pete wants to make me happy.

632
00:41:04,320 --> 00:41:08,450
So it's also not wrong if I want to do everything I can for Pete's happiness, right?

633
00:41:10,677 --> 00:41:12,607
Auntie, you knew...

634
00:41:17,617 --> 00:41:19,307
Who came?

635
00:41:20,710 --> 00:41:21,670
Who came?

636
00:41:21,670 --> 00:41:24,440
Khun Putch. Khun DeLi's here.

637
00:41:37,421 --> 00:41:40,051
Happy birthday, Auntie.

638
00:41:40,670 --> 00:41:44,340
How many times have I told you that you don't need to bring a gift, dear?

639
00:41:44,340 --> 00:41:45,920
Just your feelings is enough.

640
00:41:45,920 --> 00:41:52,120
I can't do that. Last year, I wasn't able to come. So this year, I have to be able to give it to you myself.

641
00:41:52,120 --> 00:41:55,410
Oh! My mother also wanted me to give you her regards too, Auntie.

642
00:41:55,410 --> 00:41:58,830
