667
00:43:22,150 --> 00:43:24,270
Gucci!

668
00:43:24,270 --> 00:43:26,060
Thank you very much for...

669
00:43:26,060 --> 00:43:28,032
Help...

670
00:43:28,032 --> 00:43:29,912
Ai...

671
